text: @WhiteHouse @realDonaldTrump @GovMurphy Murphy, like every Governor, knows he has to kiss Trump’s ass to get needed medical supplies from the federal government. It’s a disgusting abuse of power by Trump & a sign of what a weak person & president he is. No one buys the obsequious sound bites in Trump’s ads. #covid19
